<center><h1> Situation Metaphor (Contd) </h1>

<h2><u> Functional Development </u> </h2></center>
<h2>

The functional features of the source metaphor are the building blocks for

imposing a structure on the enormous problem space found in the Target

area. These functional features include  Spatial Identity, Temporal

Identity, Activity Identity, Filing Information, Linking and Navigation,

Filtering Information, Visualization etc.
 
</h2>






